"{\"uid\": \"nytimes.com-athletic-5404750-2024-04-10-uswnt-olympic-roster-prediction-shebelieves\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympics    As the interim head coach era of the U.S. women's national team comes to a close, it's time for a fresh round of evaluating who's in and who's out of Olympic roster contention.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In less than four months, new head coach Emma Hayes will have to select just 18 players to take to France.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Hayes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0381861778945873e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former USWNT midfielder Sam Mewis recently described the math equation she used when she was trying to figure out if she was in contention for a roster.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Mewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Mewis\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Mewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Mewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mewis would make her own depth chart, writing out the defenders, midfielders, and forwards in her hotel room.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@sammymewytalks@rogbennettthrough the \\\"math equation\\\" she used to go through to figure out who might make a USWNT roster for a major tournament \\ud83d\\ude02  \\ud83c\\udfa7Our full breakdown of the 2-1 SheBelieves semifinal victory over Japan is available now wherever you get your pods \\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8\\ud83d\\udd25pic.twitter.com/a4CSA71jnG  - The Women's Game (@WomensGameMIB)April 6, 2024    It's likely the current U.S. group is doing the math now after two SheBelieves games, with both requiring comeback victories and the team needing penalties - again - to dispatch Canada.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992342055, \"rank\": 7.661365691451647e-10, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women