vidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9906434207125594, \"rank\": 0.009444951725337417, \"text\": \"Davidson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davidson_Wildcats_men's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all know that nothing is guaranteed as a new coach comes in.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think everyone (is) trying to put their best foot forward but also understanding that it is an unorthodox time for both us as players and the coaching staff, the technical staff as a whole.\\\"\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we guess at our Olympic roster 2.0 (see our first edition here), interim head coach Twila Kilgore's summary of any roster construction provides good context.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.335504565014376e-12, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not about young or old or less experienced or more experienced.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about getting the right combinations of players with the right amount of experience and different strengths and weaknesses where they can cover each other in different areas and also have some chemistry and make sure that they are all able to highlight their strengths,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that SheBelieves is over, andZambia has officially completedthe USWNT's Olympic group, it's up to Hayes to determine the final roster - with just two international windows to do 